# Per-run working directory written by `run.sh`. Contains the
# Xdebug `.xt` trace, the captured stub-ingest JSON, and the
# per-test `php.ini` files. Useful for re-running `compare.py`
# without re-invoking PHP, but never part of git history — the
# `.xt` file alone can be tens of MiB on a real workload, and
# the JSON is regenerated on every `run.sh` invocation.
last-run/
